<div class="container">
<div class="ms-row ms-row-two ms-text" id="partial_2">
  <div class="ms-col-content">
    <p>Digital platforms are marvellous. </p>
  </div>
  <div class="ms-col-marginal">
    
  </div>
</div>
<div class="ms-row ms-row-two ms-text" id="partial_3">
