  <div class="ms-col-content">
    <p><em>The Strategic Guide to Responsible Platform Business</em> is meant to give decision-makers in platform firms concrete guidance on how to improve their organisation’s societal impact. As such, it provides 32 examples and five in-depth case studies to illustrate what more responsible approaches to platform business models and functionalities look like. These illustrations cut across a total of 17 companies, listed below. Readers can click on the strategies next to a company’s name to be directed to the sections in the Guide where this organisation is mentioned.</p>
