<div class="ms-row ms-row-two ms-text" id="partial_47">
  <div class="ms-col-content">
    <p>This <em>Strategic Guide to Responsible Platform Business</em> represents the project’s key output for practice and policy. As such, it generates advice for platform companies and their stakeholders, often inspired by the ideas of co-determination (Mitbestimmung). In preparation of this Guide, platform organisations and third parties like unions, experts, and policymakers were involved through comprehensive knowledge transfer through roundtables, workshops and reviews.</p>
